Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON MASTER GENERAL BARAN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the Dragon Legion's handiwork.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So while we were fighting Flazzard,\Nthey destroyed Carl Kingdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order of Carl was said\Nto be the greatest! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's corpse should be\Naround the palace. I'd like to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was the lead knight\Nof this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The knight Horkins was a hero whose name\Nwas known even in neighboring countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He fought off the Dragons valiantly,\Nbut the enemy Legion Commander killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother matched him\Nin skill with a sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then he...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You sheath your sword?! You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With one shot, he killed my brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There. I can't get him out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The same shape as Dai's mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve you?! Destroy the human world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I make no joke about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what the Dragon Knights\Nwere born to do after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I shall tell you\Nin place of the Dragon Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Long ago, when the gods\Nnewly created the world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}three races ruled the land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Specifically, the humans,\NDarklings, and Dragons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These days Dragons\Nare considered a type of monster,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but they used to be smarter than humans,\Nand most of them could speak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But these three races fought\Nbloody battles for control of the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gods, lamenting this,\Ndecided someone must oversee this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gods of Dragons, Darklings, and humans\Nconvened and came to a decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To create a being with the strength of\NDragons, the Magic Power of Darklings,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the heart of humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To create the ultimate warrior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is the Dragon Knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:05:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, if any race should ever\Nhold ambitions to dominate the world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it is the Dragon Knight's duty to wipe\Nthem out and administer divine punishment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nisn't Dark King Ban worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The evil is the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban seeks to wipe out the humans\Nfor the sake of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You must promptly embrace\Nthe proper duties of a Dragon Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and offer your power to King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm on the humans' side\Nno matter what anybody says!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than serve the Dark Army\Nthat took Master Aban's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Legion Commander Baran,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no effect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not harm you,\Nbut if this is how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take you with me by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible! How can this be?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on down there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense it. A being with massive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That crest...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's a Dragon Knight, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's part of the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Legion Commander Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Dark Army\Nhas their own Dragon Knight, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Only one Dragon Knight\Nis supposed to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the one true\NDragon Knight of this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But, while only one Dragon Knight\Nis supposed to be born,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to embrace your duties\Nas a Dragon Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy the humans with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never do that!\NDon't make me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Things may be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,During childhood, a Dragon Knight\Nis no different from a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you grow and begin to exhibit\Nthe Power of Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the humans will begin to fear,\Nreject, and persecute you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens,\Nyou will be the one to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! He's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw your nonsense! Dai is our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what he is,\Nwe'll never persecute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Help you destroy the humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai would...\NDai would rather die than do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, cast Behoma on Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll try to deal with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad to see someone\Noverestimate themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Betan!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Behoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! That should heal Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My greatest spell\Nthat took down three Green Dragons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought a Legion Commander\Nwho leads Dragons to be weaker than one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your resistance is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't have Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be the same race, but that\Ndoesn't give you the right to take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have... the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy... is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I said this boy is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His real name is Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He's lying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Son? Dai is your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying you're Dai's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai told me he washed up\Non Dermline Island as an infant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got any proof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The crest on his forehead is proof itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one person in the world aside from me\Ncould have the Dragon Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The son I lost 11 years ago, Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, yours is the only\NDragon Knight bloodline?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No friends or brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What about his mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the woman who gave birth to Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed the boy does bear\Na resemblance to his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that's no concern to you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Astonishing! So Baran is Dai's father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's father and son Dragon Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. It's the tearful reunion\Nof a father and son in over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget that I'm the one\Nwho set up this emotional moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I uncovered the truth\Nthat some coward was hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Dark King Ban\Nshall now grace us with his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Contain yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Up close, the pressure from him\Nis as powerful as ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see things are getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There has been debate as to\Nwhether or not Dai is a Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I went to ascertain\Nthe truth as a neutral party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Hadorra was dead set against it.\NCould he have known Dai's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These dirty little...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, what do you think\Nof the boy's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave Flazzard the most powerful armour\Nin my army to test Dai's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He possesses all manner\Nof terrifying power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I could have\Ntwo Dragon Knights under my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran must be rewarded\Nif he succeeds in recruiting Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. If he does,\Nhe may take the seat of Dark Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My decision has been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I was afraid of has come true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is why Hadorra was desperate\Nto keep Dai from Baran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems things will not go that smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Dino with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand? I'm far stronger\Nthan you could ever hope to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have... my final weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. What Matorif said...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hero's weapon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only weapon I have left\Nthat might work on you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is what lets me face any powerful enemy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my courage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only hope now\Nis that Dai defeats Baran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the name my Grampa gave to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I fight the Dark Army! I'm Dai, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the legendary Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil? Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Dragon Knight wipes us out,\Nit would be humanity's own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall call you\Nyour human name, "Dai."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! I shall defeat you\Nas a Hero who fights with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will not submit to me,\Nyou shall die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, here's a {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Behoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I get\Nmy stamina back, I'm useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spells don't seem to have\Nany effect on him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I hope you have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Any small attack\Nand he'll kill me for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to finish him\Nwith my biggest, strongest attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were hiding something,\Nbut I see it's just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aban Strash," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you unite the power, speed,\Nand Aura control, of your sword skills
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to complete that attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires spirit,\Ntechnique, and strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For a human attack, it's formidable. But\Nyou've already seen it won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He analyzed Master Aban's greatest attack\Nwith just one hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll have to use that attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please! Power of Dragons\Nthat lies within me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Awaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't defeat him,\Nall humanity will be wiped out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai showed the crest as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He blocked it?!\NEven though Dai's Strash was perfected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's absorbing the energy\Nof the Raiden spell with his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive that you can control\Nthe Power of Dragons this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, a Dragon Knight cannot control\Nthe power of the Crest until fully grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been blessed\Nwith good teachers and good battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For that spirit and courage,\NI shall show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just how terrifying it is when\Na true Dragon Knight controls the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Gigaden!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Gigabreak!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster! How dare you strike Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to do any damage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall face that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast King Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! We're in deep trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the Beast King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With you here it's like having an army...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy, you're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you should be aware\Nof what will happen if you fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that is something I'm prepared to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and rescue Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't bother.\N-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut he's completely immune to spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to damage him is\Nwith physical attacks by hand or weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Beast King. So you realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why stand in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I not reclaim my own son?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Dai doesn't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you've completely\Nsided with the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing. Of all the Legion\NCommanders, I respected you the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy, Hyunckel, wasn't bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With his hate for humans\Nin that heart of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But, everyone I favor leaves the Dark Amy.\NI guess Hadorra just lacks charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about Hyunckel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was willing to die\Nfor Hadorra or Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A true warrior\Nwill sacrifice himself for his master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's changed is that\NI now support Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you would fight me? To protect Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Dai, both Hyunckel and I\Nwould have wandered the dark path forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the sun that brought light\Nto our hearts of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All living things need the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,None can be allowed to take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be strong enough,\Nbut I will still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To move the heart\Nof one such as Crocodine this much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A child of the sun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why sheath your sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine,\NI see there's no changing your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you fight me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you will learn the terror\Nof fighting a true Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The completed Power of Dragons\Nfar beyond that of Dai's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?! His Aura is staggering,\Nbut he's just standing there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Won't you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't fight,\NI'll just have to claim your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-Impossible!\NMy axe is the one that shattered!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the secret\Nto the Dragon Knights' supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Draconic Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:25.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:32.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:44.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:46.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:52.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:57.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:01.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:08.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:13.89,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
